audio_clips.label: Cat flies towards the camera, falls on the ground and jumps again towards the camera.
First clip shows a small grey fluffy cat jumping from a small green wooden carriage. The carriage has a pot of flowers on top and is supported by wooden wheels. This carriage is placed on the grass.
Another clip shows a white and brown kitten moving its tongue during its sleep. The cat mimics drinking liquids such as water or milk.
Next clip contains a black and white kitten failing to drink water from a white plastic straw which is placed in a transparent tall glass of water.
A black striped white baby cat is drinking milk from a baby bottle. It keeps trying to get a hold of the baby bottle using its paws.
A man holding a broom is cleaning the floor. A white cat is lying on the floor and the man removes the cat using the broom and a dustpan. He then puts the cat in a trash bin.
A deer is licking the neck of a white and black cat.
A dark brown overweight cat is on the bottom of an empty white bathtub. It seems to be struggling to get out of it but keeps slipping down the walls of the tub.

Two  identical brown cats walk side by side on a light brown carpet. One of them suddenly stops and the other looks at it. After a while they both stand on their back legs, they hold each other's paws and start moving them through the air.
A grey kitten is being held by someone on a white sheet. The person holding the cat is feeding it milk by using a syringe. The kitten is drinking milk and moving her paws very fast.

A big white cat with black spots is walking towards the owner. The owner is a man wearing glasses and a shirt with green and white squares and stripes. The man is lying on the ground with his head on a pillow. The cat goes next to the owner and does a backflip. The man is very amused.
The man starts petting the cat.
Two just born kittens are fighting over their mom's milk. The mother cat decides to look at them.
A black cat is shown next to a sink. In the sink there is a gray cat sleeping. The black cat starts licking the grey one while the person filming the video is assuming what the black cat is thinking.
A grey cat is unsuccessfully trying to go up a yellow slide but it keeps getting back to the bottom of the slide.
A man is holding a white kitten with grey stripes in his hand while feeding her milk using a baby bottle.
Two white and grey cats are shown. One of the cats is giving the other a neck massage. They both look very content.
A brown cat is shown going up a running treadmill. The cat starts walking alongside her owner who is wearing white sneakers and black trousers.

A white and black cat is being held tight in a kitchen sink. The owner who is a female wearing a black shirt is pouring soap on the cat and washing it under the running water. The cat reaches for the water handle and manages to turn it off.
The next clip shows the top half of a gray cat laying on a brown floor. The cat has its eyes closed and sometimes replies to the person speaking with little noises.

A white and black overweight cat is sleeping on a large brown leather sofa. The head of the cat is hanging outside the seat. The person making the video keeps throwing sphere like folded papers at the cat but they get no reaction.
A brown golden kitten is sitting on the carpet. An electric toothbrush is placed on the carpet as well. The cat is curious about the toothbrush and it keeps hitting the toothbrush head with its paws.
A black cat is at the top of a white slide. The cat slides down where another black cat is waiting. They both try to go up the slide.

A brown cat is lying on the wooden floor. Two automatic vacuuming robots are cleaning the floor and hitting the cat. One robot is white and grey while the other one is yellow and black. The cat is not bothered by it.
A kitten is sleeping on its back in the middle of a sofa. The sofa has stripes and a pillow on top.
A grey cat sitting on a sofa is licking the head of a brown dog sitting on the floor.
A white and black kitten is on its back on the carpet and with its paws on the bottom of a sofa. The cat drags itself on the carpet until it reaches the camera.
A brown cat is on the floor which is made of white tiles. The cat goes in circles around a bit of dirt on one of the tiles.
A man wearing a blue shirt and pyjama trousers is doing pushups on the floor A white and black cat enters the scene, stands on its two back legs and gets a hold of the person's head using it's paws.
A white cat is eating from a bowl while a kid is making yum yum sounds.
A brown and white cat is massaging a black and white dog.
A striped brown cat is on the edge of a pier. A dolphin has its head out of the water next to the cat. The cat tries to touch the dolphin's nose using its left paw.
A black cat is in a dark room sitting on a green carpet which is placed next to a door. The cat tries to open the door.
A black cat is massaging the back of what appears to be a brown donkey with a red collar.
A white cat and a brown dog are in a dog bed. The white cat is hugging the dog and licking it on the back.
A black cat is playing in between the stairs. The stairs are covered with a brown carpet. The cat tries to hold on to the top stair.
Three very similar cats are moving their heads at the same time in the same directions. The cat in front is white and black and the two in the back are white and grey and white and brown.

A patterned cat is on the floor. The floor is made out of grey tiles. The owner is talking to the cat, the cat stands up and comes to the camera. The cat touches the camera and makes a sound similar to hi.
A black kitten is stuck in the leg of a pair of blue jeans. The cat manages to get out in the end.
A white kitten is sitting on its two back legs while holding tight to a baby bottle. The owner is giving milk to the kitten.
A seemingly uninterested grey cat is on the floor. The cat suddenly jumps on the sofa, gets a hold of another cat's head and pulls it on the floor.
A white cat with black legs is sitting on a red table playing with the leaves of a plant.
A brown kitten is struggling to drink milk from a baby bottle. The cat refuses the help of the owner.
A black cat is sitting on the back of a white pig. They are outside.
A brown cat is licking a peeled banana. Tv is heard in the background.
A grey cat is playing with a roll of plastic bags by spinning it. They are hanging from a wooden drawer
An overweight black and white cat jumps on a spinning chair. The owner of the cat proceeds to rotate the chair with the cat on it.
A white cat with black ears is sitting on its back and licking its chest. The cat then starts scratching its head using its paws.
A black cat is licking a lollipop which is being held by a man.
A white kitten is walking along the topside of a drawer towards the window. It does not see that there is a gap in between the drawer and the window and falls in it.
A white kitten is struggling to walk on a white carpet.
A baby is watching cartoons from a baby chair. A black cat with white paws is sitting on top of the baby's head, petting him.
A white kitten is trying to escape a green bowl. The kitten is stuck on the top edge of the container.
The kitten falls on its head and then stands up.
A white cats prepares for a jump. The cat then jumps on the kitchen desk and slides. She falls of the table while dragging the black toaster with it.
A golden brown cat is drinking milk from a baby bottle.
A plate with brown edges and remains of ketchup and french fries is being shown. A person points a finger at the plate. Then a cat appears and takes one fry from the plate.
Screen saying funny pet videos is shown with video suggestions. The image contains drawing of cats and dogs.
